    "body": "Hi @ngan. I'd bring this up with ruby-eth. It seems to me that you've identified a network id limit (i.e., between 1 and 100), although there's no spec defining 100 as the upper limit. 4447 isn't special in its own right, but it needs to be consistent; that said, we won't want it getting confused with an official chain, so the larger the better. \n\nI'm going to close this issue. Let me know if the response from ruby-eth. Cheers! ",
